<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 03:13:28 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国将军称中国军队于2023年进行了入侵台湾演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-military-practiced-taiwan-invasion-manoeuvres-2023-says-us-general-2024-05-23/</link><description>一名驻该地区的美国高级将领周四表示，中国 2023 年在台湾海峡举行的军事演习演练了入侵该岛的关键演习，尽管实际的攻击并非迫在眉睫或不可避免。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 03:07:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-military-practiced-taiwan-invasion-manoeuvres-2023-says-us-general-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市因降息的耐心态度而走软</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-23/</link><description>由于市场消化了主要经济体政策制定者在通胀高企的情况下更愿意采取耐心的货币宽松政策的影响，几个主要的亚洲股市基准周四下跌。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 02:22:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称中国哈尔滨公寓楼发生爆炸</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/explosion-apartment-building-chinas-harbin-says-state-media-2024-05-23/</link><description>据中国官方媒体周四上午报道，中国黑龙江省省会哈尔滨市一栋五层公寓楼发生爆炸，目前没有人员伤亡报告。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 02:01:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/explosion-apartment-building-chinas-harbin-says-state-media-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>美联储鹰派会议纪要后，美元徘徊在一周高位附近</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-hovers-near-highest-week-after-hawkish-fed-minutes-2024-05-23/</link><description>周四，美元兑主要货币汇率创本月最佳表现，周四徘徊在一周高点附近，此前美联储上次会议纪要显示部分官员愿意加息。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 01:08:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-hovers-near-highest-week-after-hawkish-fed-minutes-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国开始“惩罚”演习后，台湾向岛屿周边地区派遣部队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-starts-military-drills-around-taiwan-days-after-new-president-takes-office-2024-05-23/</link><description>中国周四在台湾周围开始为期两天的“惩罚”演习，称这是对“分裂主义行为”的回应，台湾军方动员了力量，并表示有信心能够保护台湾。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 00:35:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-starts-military-drills-around-taiwan-days-after-new-president-takes-office-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>桥水基金任命中国区总裁阿尔珀特负责监管新投资部门</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bridgewater-taps-china-head-alpert-oversee-new-investment-unit-2024-05-22/</link><description>桥水基金已提拔其中国区总经理乔安娜·阿尔珀特 (Joanna Alpert) 担任最近成立的业务部门负责人，该部门专注于管理和创造新的投资产品。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 23:55:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bridgewater-taps-china-head-alpert-oversee-new-investment-unit-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞标：韩国银行紧随其后，英伟达继续前进</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-22/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 21:50:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>杜邦公司将分拆为三个公司，并更换首席执行官埃德·布林 (Ed Breen)</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/dupont-separate-into-three-independent-companies-2024-05-22/</link><description>杜邦公司周三表示，将分拆为三家上市公司，其股价在盘后上涨 5%，加入众多寻求释放价值和追求集中增长的美国企业集团行列。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 21:10:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/dupont-separate-into-three-independent-companies-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，因国家监管机构审查而推迟波音向中国交付</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-deliveries-china-delayed-by-state-regulator-review-source-says-2024-05-22/</link><description>一位知情人士告诉路透社，由于中国对驾驶舱录音机电池进行监管审查，波音向中国的飞机交付最近几周被推迟。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 19:52:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-deliveries-china-delayed-by-state-regulator-review-source-says-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>美国立法者提出法案，以更容易遏制人工智能模型的出口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-lawmakers-advance-bill-make-it-easier-curb-exports-ai-models-2024-05-22/</link><description>众议院外交事务委员会周三以压倒性多数票通过了一项法案，该法案将使拜登政府更容易限制人工智能系统的出口，理由是担心中国可能利用这些系统来增强其军事能力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 17:01:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-lawmakers-advance-bill-make-it-easier-curb-exports-ai-models-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国地方政府机构要求恒大电动汽车公司返还2.624亿美元补贴</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-local-bodies-ask-evergrande-ev-unit-return-2624-mln-subsidy-2024-05-22/</link><description>中国恒大新能源汽车周三表示，其子公司已收到中国地方行政机构的一封信，要求偿还作为补贴和奖励提供的19亿元人民币（2.6242亿美元）。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 14:19:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-local-bodies-ask-evergrande-ev-unit-return-2624-mln-subsidy-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>法国七国集团需要在中国产能过剩问题上团结一致</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/g7-needs-stand-united-chinese-overcapacity-france-2024-05-22/</link><description>法国财政部长布鲁诺·勒梅尔周三在与七国集团同行举行会议之前表示，面对中国在电动汽车电池等关键行业的产能过剩，七国集团经济强国需要团结起来。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 13:04:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/g7-needs-stand-united-chinese-overcapacity-france-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国多个城市大幅降低还款额和抵押贷款利率以刺激房地产需求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/several-chinese-cities-slash-down-payments-mortgage-rates-boost-property-demand-2024-05-22/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，中国多个城市降低了首付和抵押贷款利率，以应对最新一波刺激低迷房地产需求的刺激措施。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 11:20:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/several-chinese-cities-slash-down-payments-mortgage-rates-boost-property-demand-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>Temu母公司拼多多控股第一季度营收超出预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/temu-operator-pdd-holdings-beats-first-quarter-revenue-estimates-2024-05-22/</link><description>拼多多控股周三超出了第一季度收入预期，这得益于其国际购物网站 Temu 以及消费者对其中国折扣电子商务平台拼多多日益增长的兴趣。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 10:42:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/temu-operator-pdd-holdings-beats-first-quarter-revenue-estimates-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>流亡中国商人郭文贵因诈骗罪受审</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/exiled-chinese-businessman-guo-wengui-goes-trial-fraud-2024-05-22/</link><description>对流亡中国商人郭文贵的刑事审判将于周三开始陪审团遴选，美国检察官指控郭文贵诈骗数千名投资者和支持者超过 10 亿美元。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 10:04:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/exiled-chinese-businessman-guo-wengui-goes-trial-fraud-2024-05-22/</guid></item></channel></rss>